library(tidyverse)
data <- as.tibble(mtcars)
head(data)
data <- tibble(x = 1:3, y = c("a","b","c"), z = c("d", "e", "f"))
head(data)
data <- tribble(~x,~y,~z,
                1,"a","d",
                2,"b","e",
                3,"c","f")
head(data)
v <- c(a = 5, b = 7, c = 6)
enframe(v)
data1 <- pivot_longer(data, cols = c("y", "z"), names_to = "name", values_to = "value")
data1
pivot_wider(data1, names_from = "name", values_from = "value")
data1 <- unite(data, "x", "y", col = "xy", sep = " ")
data1
separate(data1, "xy", sep = " ", into = c("x", "y"))
separate_rows(data1, "xy", sep = " ")
data <- tibble(x1 = c("A", "B", "B"), x2 = c(1,1,2), x3 = c(3,4,3))
data
expand(data, x1, x2)
complete(data, x1, x2)
storms
n_storms <- storms %>% 
  group_by(name) %>% 
  nest()
n_storms$data[[1]]
n_storms <- storms %>% 
  nest(data = -name)
n_storms$data[[1]]
n_storms %>% 
  unnest(data)
row_fn <- n_storms %>% 
 rowwise() %>%
 mutate(n = list(dim(data)))
row_fn$data[[1]]
row_fn$n[[1]]
[1] 30 12
row_fn <- n_storms %>% 
 rowwise() %>%
 mutate(n = nrow(data))
row_fn
x <- tibble(A = c("a", "b", "c"), B = c("t", "u", "v"), C = c(1,2,3))
y <- tibble(A = c("a", "b", "d"), B = c("t", "u", "w"), D = c(3,2,1))
left_join(x, y)

Joining, by = c("A", "B")
right_join(x, y)
Joining, by = c("A", "B")
inner_join(x, y)
Joining, by = c("A", "B")
full_join(x, y)
Joining, by = c("A", "B")
semi_join(x, y)
Joining, by = c("A", "B")
anti_join(x, y)
Joining, by = c("A", "B")
